        <p>Vienna, famous for a lot of culuturous sites, has a 2000 year history in winemaking. Still today, there are almost 600 ha under vines planted.</p>
        <p>Dominant are white grape varieties such as Gruner Veltliner, Riesling, Weissburgunder among a few others. Red varieties consist of Zweigelt,</p>
        <p>St. Laurent pre-dominantly. The majority of the wines produced is dry or off-dry. Vast majority produced for consumption within 2 - 5 years.</p>
